  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, javax.xml.transform.SourceLocator, ExpressionNode, ExpressionOwner, XPathVisitable

    public class FuncLang
extends FunctionMultiArgs
    Implementation of fn:lang function (available in both XPath 1.0 and 3.1 versions). XPath 3.1 has introduced an optional second argument for this function, representing an explicit XPath node. The meaning of first argument of this function is same, within both XPath 1.0 and 3.1 versions.
